      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The poster shows a scene from the film ‘Karadjordje. Život i dela besmrtnog vožda Karadjordja’ (The life and deeds of the immortal leader Karadjordje), with Karadjorde in the centre.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The poster was created to celebrate the 100th anniversary of Serbian feature film in 2011. The first Serbian feature was assumed lost until experts discovered a copy in Austria’s ‘Film Archiv’ in 2003. The copy was restored and screened on Serbian TV.</ab>
